      "start": 670.87,
      "end": 673.11,
      "text": "저는 굉장히 간지러움을 많이 타는 사람입니다"
    },
    {
      "start": 673.11,
      "end": 673.81,
      "text": "Same here"
    },
    {
      "start": 673.81,
      "end": 674.51,
      "text": "진짜요"
    },
    {
      "start": 674.51,
      "end": 675.45,
      "text": "If you just touch me"
    },
    {
      "start": 675.45,
      "end": 675.71,
      "text": "Yeah"
    },
    {
      "start": 675.71,
      "end": 677.29,
      "text": "Oh, 그래요"
    },
    {
      "start": 677.29,
      "end": 679.49,
      "text": "Tickle 하면 간지럼 태우다"
    },
    {
      "start": 679.49,
      "end": 680.45,
      "text": "라는 동사거든요"
    },
    {
      "start": 680.45,
      "end": 681.07,
      "text": "그래서"
    },
    {
      "start": 681.07,
      "end": 682.43,
      "text": "Tickle our bellies"
    },
    {
      "start": 682.43,
      "end": 683.01,
      "text": "라고 했으니까"
    },
    {
      "start": 683.01,
      "end": 685.03,
      "text": "우리의 배를 간질간질이거나"
    },
    {
      "start": 685.03,
      "end": 687.97,
      "text": "And laugh when we eat peanut butter"
    },
    {
      "start": 687.97,
      "end": 688.63,
      "text": "이라고 했어요"
    },
    {
      "start": 688.63,
      "end": 691.41,
      "text": "우리가 땅콩 버터를 먹을 때"
    },
    {
      "start": 691.41,
      "end": 693.87,
      "text": "우리를 보며 웃게 내버려두고 말이야"
    },
    {
      "start": 693.87,
      "end": 694.43,
      "text": "라는 거예요"
    },
    {
      "start": 694.43,
      "end": 697.01,
      "text": "I used to put peanut butter"
    },
    {
      "start": 697.01,
      "end": 697.81,
      "text": "once in a while"
    },
    {
      "start": 697.81,
      "end": 699.49,
      "text": "in a doggy treat"
    },
    {
      "start": 699.49,
      "end": 700.93,
      "text": "Why did you do that?"
    },
    {
      "start": 700.93,
      "end": 701.71,
      "text": "A doggy ball"
    },
    {
      "start": 701.71,
      "end": 703.87,
      "text": "If my dog was being a good dog"
    },
    {
      "start": 703.87,
      "end": 704.85,
      "text": "there's a little"
    },
    {
      "start": 704.85,
      "end": 705.95,
      "text": "like a hollow ball"
    },
    {
      "start": 705.95,
      "end": 706.65,
      "text": "It's kind of a reward"
    },
    {
      "start": 706.65,
      "end": 707.13,
      "text": "Yeah"
    },
    {
      "start": 707.13,
      "end": 708.53,
      "text": "And you put the peanut butter"
    },
    {
      "start": 708.53,
      "end": 709.15,
      "text": "in the ball"
    },
    {
      "start": 709.15,
      "end": 711.05,
      "text": "And then you give it to the dog"
    },
    {
      "start": 711.05,
      "end": 712.59,
      "text": "And he pushes it all over"
    },
    {
      "start": 712.59,
      "end": 713.69,
      "text": "the backyard"
    },
    {
      "start": 713.69,
      "end": 714.53,
      "text": "Not inside"
    },
    {
      "start": 714.53,
      "end": 715.79,
      "text": "Inside would be a mess"
    },
    {
      "start": 715.79,
      "end": 716.17,
      "text": "그렇죠"
    },
    {
      "start": 716.17,
      "end": 717.97,
      "text": "아, 땅콩 버터를"
    },
    {
      "start": 717.97,
      "end": 719.51,
      "text": "미국에서는 강아지들한테"
    },
    {
      "start": 719.51,
      "end": 720.97,
      "text": "약간 보상으로다가"
    },
    {
      "start": 720.97,
      "end": 722.31,
      "text": "가끔 주기도 하나 봐요"
    },
    {
      "start": 722.31,
      "end": 723.15,
      "text": "Once in a while"
    },
    {
      "start": 723.15,
      "end": 724.51,
      "text": "You know it's rich"
    },
    {
      "start": 724.51,
      "end": 724.95,
      "text": "Yeah"
    },
    {
      "start": 724.95,
      "end": 725.97,
      "text": "And if they eat it every day"
    },
    {
      "start": 725.97,
      "end": 726.71,
      "text": "Too much fat"
    },
    {
      "start": 726.71,
      "end": 727.01,
      "text": "Yeah"
    },
    {
      "start": 727.01,
      "end": 727.89,
      "text": "They won't be healthy"
    },
    {
      "start": 727.89,
      "end": 728.21,
      "text": "그렇죠"
    },
    {
      "start": 728.21,
      "end": 729.29,
      "text": "They'll get fat and lazy"
    },
    {
      "start": 729.29,
      "end": 729.71,
      "text": "Yeah"
    },
    {
      "start": 729.71,
      "end": 731.33,
      "text": "Just as a special reward"
    },
    {
      "start": 731.33,
      "end": 731.95,
      "text": "오, 그래"
    },
    {
      "start": 731.95,
      "end": 733.11,
      "text": "가뭄에 콩나듯"
    },
    {
      "start": 733.11,
      "end": 733.95,
      "text": "주는 것은 뭐"
    },
    {
      "start": 733.95,
      "end": 735.03,
      "text": "괜찮을 것 같긴 한데"
    },
    {
      "start": 735.03,
      "end": 735.77,
      "text": "어쨌든"
    },
    {
      "start": 735.77,
      "end": 736.25,
      "text": "Yeah"
    },
    {
      "start": 736.25,
      "end": 737.55,
      "text": "Keeping them healthy"
    },
    {
      "start": 737.55,
      "end": 738.39,
      "text": "and safe"
    },
    {
      "start": 738.39,
      "end": 739.37,
      "text": "is very important"
    },
    {
      "start": 739.37,
      "end": 740.29,
      "text": "The most important"
    },
    {
      "start": 740.29,
      "end": 740.73,
      "text": "Yeah"
    },
    {
      "start": 740.73,
      "end": 741.47,
      "text": "And"
    },
    {
      "start": 741.47,
      "end": 742.39,
      "text": "오, 하나 더 있어요"
    },
    {
      "start": 742.39,
      "end": 742.89,
      "text": "오, 그래요?"
    },
    {
      "start": 743.39,
      "end": 745.33,
      "text": "Hug us when they're sad"
    },
    {
      "start": 745.33,
      "end": 746.59,
      "text": "많이 있네요"
    },
    {
      "start": 746.59,
      "end": 748.49,
      "text": "Hug us when they're sad"
    },
    {
      "start": 748.49,
      "end": 749.55,
      "text": "We will let them"
    },
    {
      "start": 749.55,
      "end": 750.35,
      "text": "hug us"
    },
    {
      "start": 750.35,
      "end": 751.75,
      "text": "when they are sad"
    },
    {
      "start": 751.75,
      "end": 753.07,
      "text": "I feel sympathy"
    },
    {
      "start": 753.07,
      "end": 754.29,
      "text": "with this"
    },
    {
      "start": 754.29,
      "end": 755.71,
      "text": "너무 공감되는 말입니다"
    },
    {
      "start": 755.71,
      "end": 756.75,
      "text": "인간이 슬프면"
    },
    {
      "start": 756.75,
      "end": 757.07,
      "text": "Yeah"
    },
    {
      "start": 757.07,
      "end": 758.45,
      "text": "좀 안아주게 해줘"
    },
    {
      "start": 758.45,
      "end": 759.47,
      "text": "그들이 슬플 땐"
    },
    {
      "start": 759.47,
      "end": 761.21,
      "text": "우리를 안게 해주는 거야"
    },
    {
      "start": 761.21,
      "end": 762.71,
      "text": "라는 말이었어요"
    },
    {
      "start": 762.71,
      "end": 763.39,
      "text": "How sweet"
    },
    {
      "start": 763.39,
      "end": 765.33,
      "text": "They are above us"
    },
    {
      "start": 765.33,
      "end": 766.39,
      "text": "They're way above us"
    },
    {
      "start": 766.39,
      "end": 768.17,
      "text": "Shut up, kid"
    },
    {
      "start": 768.17,
      "end": 768.97,
      "text": "네"
    },
    {
      "start": 768.97,
      "end": 769.99,
      "text": "갑자기 찬물을"
    },
    {
      "start": 769.99,
      "end": 771.17,
      "text": "누가 확 끼얹었어요"
    },
    {
      "start": 771.17,
      "end": 771.81,
      "text": "라우지가"
    },
    {
      "start": 771.81,
      "end": 773.31,
      "text": "Shut up, kid"
    },
    {
      "start": 773.31,
      "end": 774.01,
      "text": "라고 했어요"
    },
    {
      "start": 774.01,
      "end": 774.43,
      "text": "Kid"
    },
    {
      "start": 774.43,
      "end": 775.27,
      "text": "그만해"
    },
    {
      "start": 775.27,
      "end": 776.39,
      "text": "라는 이야기입니다"
    },
    {
      "start": 776.39,
      "end": 777.15,
      "text": "아, kid"
    },
    {
      "start": 777.15,
      "end": 778.19,
      "text": "kid 부리면"
    },
    {
      "start": 778.19,
      "end": 779.75,
      "text": "약간 무시하는"
    },
    {
      "start": 779.75,
      "end": 780.47,
      "text": "그런 것 같아요"
    },
    {
      "start": 780.47,
      "end": 780.77,
      "text": "미얀지죠"
    },
    {
      "start": 780.77,
      "end": 781.83,
      "text": "Shut up, kid"
    },
    {
      "start": 781.83,
      "end": 785.43,
      "text": "And all they ask for in return"
    },
    {
      "start": 785.43,
      "end": 787.99,
      "text": "All they ask for in return"
    },
    {
      "start": 787.99,
      "end": 789.03,
      "text": "여기서 in return"
    },
    {
      "start": 789.03,
      "end": 789.67,
      "text": "이라는 것은"
    },
    {
      "start": 789.67,
      "end": 790.73,
      "text": "대신에"
    },
    {
      "start": 790.73,
      "end": 791.73,
      "text": "답예로"
    },
    {
      "start": 791.73,
      "end": 792.57,
      "text": "보답으로"
    },
    {
      "start": 792.57,
      "end": 793.49,
      "text": "라는 의미잖아요"
    },
    {
      "start": 793.49,
      "end": 794.19,
      "text": "그래서"
    },
    {
      "start": 794.19,
      "end": 795.51,
      "text": "주인이"
    },
    {
      "start": 795.51,
      "end": 796.07,
      "text": "대신에"
    },
    {
      "start": 796.07,
      "end": 797.53,
      "text": "우리에게 바라는 건"
    },
    {
      "start": 797.53,
      "end": 798.53,
      "text": "이라는 해석입니다"
    },
    {
      "start": 798.53,
      "end": 799.35,
      "text": "아, 그 강의를"
    },
    {
      "start": 799.35,
      "end": 799.89,
      "text": "계속"
    },
    {
      "start": 799.89,
      "end": 800.73,
      "text": "하려고 하는데"
    },
    {
      "start": 800.73,
      "end": 802.75,
      "text": "I said quit it"
    },
    {
      "start": 802.75,
      "end": 803.15,
      "text": "그랬더니"
    },
    {
      "start": 803.15,
      "end": 803.65,
      "text": "라우지가"
    },
    {
      "start": 803.65,
      "end": 804.87,
      "text": "I said quit it"
    },
    {
      "start": 804.87,
      "end": 805.39,
      "text": "내가"
    },
    {
      "start": 805.39,
      "end": 806.73,
      "text": "그만하라고 했잖아"
    },
    {
      "start": 806.73,
      "end": 807.63,
      "text": "라고 소리를"
    },
    {
      "start": 807.63,
      "end": 808.63,
      "text": "한 번 더 지르죠"
    },
    {
      "start": 808.63,
      "end": 809.83,
      "text": "그만하라니까"
    },
    {
      "start": 809.83,
      "end": 811.19,
      "text": "quit it"
    },
    {
      "start": 811.19,
      "end": 811.99,
      "text": "I said quit it"
    },
    {
      "start": 811.99,
      "end": 813.11,
      "text": "I said quit it"
    },
    {
      "start": 813.11,
      "end": 814.67,
      "text": "How many times do I have to say it?"
    },
    {
      "start": 814.67,
      "end": 815.25,
      "text": "그만하라고"
    },
    {
      "start": 815.25,
      "end": 816.23,
      "text": "I said quit it"
    },
    {
      "start": 816.23,
      "end": 817.53,
      "text": "계속 할 수 있죠"
    },
    {
      "start": 817.53,
      "end": 817.79,
      "text": "이거"
    },
    {
      "start": 817.79,
      "end": 818.71,
      "text": "이거 좋아요"
    },
    {
      "start": 818.71,
      "end": 820.37,
      "text": "쓸모가 많아요"
    },
    {
      "start": 820.37,
      "end": 823.39,
      "text": "Is that we give them"
    },
    {
      "start": 823.39,
      "end": 824.93,
      "text": "unconditional love"
    },
    {
      "start": 824.93,
      "end": 825.93,
      "text": "Wow, 정말 중요한"
    },
    {
      "start": 825.93,
      "end": 826.99,
      "text": "He's finishing his sentence"
    },
    {
      "start": 826.99,
      "end": 829.93,
      "text": "와, 너무 사랑스러운 멘트였어요"
    },
    {
      "start": 829.93,
      "end": 831.29,
      "text": "Is that we give them"
    },
    {
      "start": 831.29,
      "end": 832.91,
      "text": "unconditional love"
    },
    {
      "start": 832.91,
      "end": 835.61,
      "text": "무조건적으로"
    },
    {
      "start": 835.61,
      "end": 837.95,
      "text": "그들을 따르는 것일 뿐이야"
    },
    {
      "start": 837.95,
      "end": 839.17,
      "text": "라는 이야기입니다"
    },
    {
      "start": 839.17,
      "end": 840.41,
      "text": "That's all the humans"
    },
    {
      "start": 840.41,
      "end": 841.21,
      "text": "us humans"
    },
    {
      "start": 841.21,
      "end": 842.75,
      "text": "ask for in return"
    },
    {
      "start": 842.75,
      "end": 843.25,
      "text": "맞아요"
    },
    {
      "start": 843.25,
      "end": 844.63,
      "text": "Just to love us unconditionally"
    },
    {
      "start": 844.63,
      "end": 845.71,
      "text": "너무 감동적이었습니다"
    },
    {
      "start": 845.71,
      "end": 848.69,
      "text": "이 장면 한 번 더 들어보시죠"
    },
    {
      "start": 848.93,
      "end": 850.77,
      "text": "We're supposed to be there for our owners"
    },
    {
      "start": 850.77,
      "end": 852.19,
      "text": "Let them play with us"
    },
    {
      "start": 852.19,
      "end": 853.15,
      "text": "and feed us"
    },
    {
      "start": 853.15,
      "end": 854.47,
      "text": "Call us silly names"
    },
    {
      "start": 854.47,
      "end": 855.63,
      "text": "throw balls for us"
    },
    {
      "start": 855.63,
      "end": 857.21,
      "text": "Keep us healthy and safe"
    },
    {
      "start": 857.21,
      "end": 858.63,
      "text": "Tickle our bellies"
    },
    {
      "start": 858.63,
      "end": 859.43,
      "text": "and laugh when we eat"
    },
    {
      "start": 859.43,
      "end": 860.05,
      "text": "peanut butter"
    },
    {
      "start": 860.05,
      "end": 861.49,
      "text": "Hug us when they're sad"
    },
    {
      "start": 861.49,
      "end": 862.55,
      "text": "Shut up, kid"
    },
    {
      "start": 862.55,
      "end": 864.53,
      "text": "And all they ask for in return"
    },
    {
      "start": 864.53,
      "end": 866.07,
      "text": "I said quit it"
    },
    {
      "start": 866.07,
      "end": 867.29,
      "text": "Is that we give them"
    },
    {
      "start": 867.29,
      "end": 868.93,
      "text": "unconditional love"
    },
    {
      "start": 868.93,
      "end": 872.8,
      "text": "사실 이렇게 반려동물들을"
    },
    {
      "start": 872.8,
      "end": 873.92,
      "text": "기르는 일에는"
    },
    {
      "start": 873.92,
      "end": 876.0,
      "text": "정말 it takes a big responsibility"
    },
    {
      "start": 876.0,
      "end": 876.92,
      "text": "right?"
    },
    {
      "start": 877.14,
      "end": 877.86,
      "text": "Yes, definitely"
    },
    {
      "start": 877.86,
      "end": 879.04,
      "text": "그중에도"
    },
    {
      "start": 879.04,
      "end": 880.9,
      "text": "동물병원에 관련되어서"
    },
    {
      "start": 880.9,
      "end": 882.32,
      "text": "병원비가 엄청 비싸잖아요"
    },
    {
      "start": 882.32,
      "end": 884.4,
      "text": "저도 강아지를 키웠을 때는"
    },
    {
      "start": 884.4,
      "end": 885.74,
      "text": "정기적으로 가서"
    },
    {
      "start": 885.74,
      "end": 887.24,
      "text": "여러가지 예방접종도"
    },
    {
      "start": 887.24,
      "end": 888.72,
      "text": "엄청 자주 마쳤고"
    },
    {
      "start": 888.72,
      "end": 889.44,
      "text": "Vaccinations"
    },
    {
      "start": 889.44,
      "end": 890.0,
      "text": "치료도 하고"
    },
    {
      "start": 890.0,
      "end": 892.12,
      "text": "치료도 하고"
    },
    {
      "start": 892.12,
      "end": 894.24,
      "text": "근데 it was really expensive"
    },
    {
      "start": 894.24,
      "end": 895.72,
      "text": "It is"
    },
    {
      "start": 895.72,
      "end": 897.28,
      "text": "Yeah, beyond my expectation"
    },
    {
      "start": 897.28,
      "end": 899.52,
      "text": "I think it's even more expensive"
    },
    {
      "start": 899.52,
      "end": 900.64,
      "text": "in the US"
    },
    {
      "start": 900.64,
      "end": 902.1,
      "text": "Oh, yeah"
    },
    {
      "start": 902.1,
      "end": 904.1,
      "text": "그만만큼 엄청난 책임감이"
    },
    {
      "start": 904.1,
      "end": 905.52,
      "text": "필요하다라는 거"
    },
    {
      "start": 905.52,
      "end": 907.02,
      "text": "짚어드리고 싶었습니다"
    },
    {
      "start": 907.02,
      "end": 909.02,
      "text": "Even to adopt a dog"
    },
    {
      "start": 909.02,
      "end": 909.78,
      "text": "from the pound"
    },
    {
      "start": 909.78,
      "end": 911.46,
      "text": "You don't pay for the dog"
    },
    {
      "start": 911.46,
      "end": 912.1,
      "text": "itself"
    },
    {
      "start": 912.1,
      "end": 912.88,
      "text": "It's free"
    },
    {
      "start": 912.88,
      "end": 913.9,
      "text": "But you have to pay for"
    },
    {
      "start": 913.9,
      "end": 914.6,
      "text": "all the shots"
    },
    {
      "start": 914.6,
      "end": 915.62,
      "text": "and checkups"
    },
    {
      "start": 915.62,
      "end": 917.06,
      "text": "before they go home with you"
    },
    {
      "start": 917.06,
      "end": 918.98,
      "text": "And that is a lot of money"
    },
    {
      "start": 918.98,
      "end": 920.62,
      "text": "아주 중요한 포인트까지"
    },
    {
      "start": 920.62,
      "end": 921.48,
      "text": "짚어드립니다"
    },
    {
      "start": 921.48,
      "end": 922.86,
      "text": "Be responsible dog owners"
    },
    {
      "start": 922.86,
      "end": 923.12,
      "text": "Yeah"
    },
    {
      "start": 923.12,
      "end": 925.32,
      "text": "자, 오늘 여기에서 마무리할게요"
    },
    {
      "start": 925.32,
      "end": 925.88,
      "text": "그루스 씨"
    },
    {
      "start": 925.88,
      "end": 926.78,
      "text": "내일 또 만나요"
    }
  ]
}